---
---
<section class="reveal py-[52.8px] bg-gray-50">
  <div class="max-w-[1340px] w-full mx-auto px-[10px]">
    <div class="text-center mb-16">
      <h2 class="font-heading text-[52.8px] font-semibold leading-[1.2] text-navy-900 mb-4">Sportswear is What We Make</h2>
      <p class="font-body text-[17.6px] leading-[1.5] text-gray-600 max-w-3xl mx-auto">We design and manufacture cutting-edge sportswear that combines style, comfort, and performance.</p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
      <!-- Service 1 -->
      <div class="bg-white p-10 rounded-xl shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow text-center group">
        <div class="h-20 flex justify-center items-center mb-6">
          <img src="/images/services/Service-1-1.png" alt="Custom Design" class="h-16 object-contain group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300" />
        </div>
        <h3 class="font-heading text-[24px] font-medium leading-[1.2] text-navy-900 mb-4">Custom Design</h3>
        <p class="font-body text-[17.6px] leading-[1.5] text-gray-600">Collaborate with our experienced designers to create unique and eye-catching sportswear designs that reflect your brand and vision.</p>
      </div>
      <!-- Service 2 -->
      <div class="bg-white p-10 rounded-xl shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow text-center group">
        <div class="h-20 flex justify-center items-center mb-6">
          <img src="/images/services/Service-2-1.png" alt="Custom Fit" class="h-16 object-contain group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300" />
        </div>
        <h3 class="font-heading text-[24px] font-medium leading-[1.2] text-navy-900 mb-4">Custom Fit</h3>
        <p class="font-body text-[17.6px] leading-[1.5] text-gray-600">Enjoy the perfect fit with our tailored sportswear options, ensuring optimal comfort and freedom of movement for athletes of all shapes and sizes.</p>
      </div>
      <!-- Service 3 -->
      <div class="bg-white p-10 rounded-xl shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow text-center group">
        <div class="h-20 flex justify-center items-center mb-6">
          <img src="/images/services/Service-3-1.png" alt="Private Label" class="h-16 object-contain group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300" />
        </div>
        <h3 class="font-heading text-[24px] font-medium leading-[1.2] text-navy-900 mb-4">Private Label</h3>
        <p class="font-body text-[17.6px] leading-[1.5] text-gray-600">Benefit from our expertise in private label manufacturing, where we can produce sportswear under your brand name, providing a seamless and professional solution.</p>
      </div>
      <!-- Service 4 -->
      <div class="bg-white p-10 rounded-xl shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow text-center group">
        <div class="h-20 flex justify-center items-center mb-6">
          <img src="/images/services/Service-4-1.png" alt="Performance Enhancement" class="h-16 object-contain group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300" />
        </div>
        <h3 class="font-heading text-[24px] font-medium leading-[1.2] text-navy-900 mb-4">Performance Enhancement</h3>
        <p class="font-body text-[17.6px] leading-[1.5] text-gray-600">Our sportswear is designed to enhance performance, incorporating advanced fabric technologies and functional features that optimize athletic abilities.</p>
      </div>
      <!-- Service 5 -->
      <div class="bg-white p-10 rounded-xl shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow text-center group">
        <div class="h-20 flex justify-center items-center mb-6">
          <img src="/images/services/Service-5-1.png" alt="Sublimation Printing" class="h-16 object-contain group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300" />
        </div>
        <h3 class="font-heading text-[24px] font-medium leading-[1.2] text-navy-900 mb-4">Sublimation Printing</h3>
        <p class="font-body text-[17.6px] leading-[1.5] text-gray-600">Experience vibrant and long-lasting graphics on your sportswear through our sublimation printing technique, allowing for unlimited design possibilities.</p>
      </div>
      <!-- Service 6 -->
      <div class="bg-white p-10 rounded-xl shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow text-center group">
        <div class="h-20 flex justify-center items-center mb-6">
          <img src="/images/services/Service-6-1.png" alt="Quick Turnaround" class="h-16 object-contain group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300" />
        </div>
        <h3 class="font-heading text-[24px] font-medium leading-[1.2] text-navy-900 mb-4">Quick Turnaround</h3>
        <p class="font-body text-[17.6px] leading-[1.5] text-gray-600">With our efficient production processes and dedicated team, we offer fast turnaround times, ensuring your sportswear is delivered promptly, even for time-sensitive projects.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
